-- Hawkin’s Bazaar Rescued From Administration, Times Reports
-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 2012-01-21T11:31:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-21/hawkin-s-bazaar-rescued-from-administration-times-reports.html
Primary Capital Limited has rescued
Hawkin’s Bazaar Shops Ltd. from administration, the London Times
reported, without saying where it got the information.  The private-equity company bought the remaining stores,
website and wholesale business of the gift retailer yesterday,
the newspaper reported. Primary Capital is the largest
shareholder in Hawkin’s Bazaar, the Times said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adam Haigh in London at 
 ahaigh1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Rummer at 
